</strong> in story mode (will be completed within the game\u2019s Early Access period).<br></li><li><strong>Challenge mode</strong> for even more adventures in the deep.<br></li><li><strong>Local co-op and Remote Play co-op already available</strong> (Online co-op will be introduced within the game\u2019s Early Access period).</li></ul>","developers":["Cogwheel Software"],"dlc":[1670550],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976890/header_alt_assets_4.jpg?t=1737396331","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 2020 Daedalic Entertainment GmbH.<br />\r\nDaedalic and the Daedalic logo are trademarks of Daedalic Entertainment GmbH, Germany.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256957844,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256957844/movie480.mp4?t=1689180292","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256957844/movie_max.mp4?t=1689180292"},"name":"Depth Survivors Update","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256957844/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1689180292","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256957844/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1689180292","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256957844/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1689180292"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256872208,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256872208/movie480.mp4?t=1644005596","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256872208/movie_max.mp4?t=1644005596"},"name":"ReactionsMontage","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256872208/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1644005596","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256872208/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1644005596","max":"http: